'''Tracy Duncan''', also known as '''Dark Spork''', '''Dunc''' or '''Snarkel''', has been active in online fandom since [[1995]]. Her vocal presence in the online fan community led her to be [[Tuckerization|tuckerized]] as [[Dunc T'racen]] in [[Tish Eggleston Pahl|Tish Pahl]] and [[Chris Cassidy]]'s short story "[[Hutt and Seek]]."

She is the webmaster of Club Jade and a former moderator on [[StarWars.com]] forums. She also runs the Livejournal communities "[http://community.livejournal.com/starwars_eu starwars_eu]" and "[http://community.livejournal.com/swrecs swrecs]."

Duncan, as [[Wookieepedia]]n {{U|Dark Spork}}, created the current Wookieepedia [[:File:Wiki.png|logo]] and the original search icon.

